TITLE: Client Instance Management in Elasticsearch .NET
DESCRIPTION: Guidance on the proper usage of ElasticsearchClient instance, emphasizing the importance of reusing a single instance throughout the application lifecycle. The client is thread-safe and can be implemented as a singleton or registered with dependency injection containers for optimal resource utilization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch-net/blob/main/docs/reference/recommendations.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
ElasticsearchClient
```

