TITLE: Connecting to Elasticsearch Cloud Deployment using .NET Client
DESCRIPTION: Creates an ElasticsearchClient instance that connects to an Elastic Cloud deployment using Cloud ID and API key authentication. This is the recommended approach for cloud deployments as it automatically configures HTTPS and HTTP compression.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch-net/blob/main/docs/reference/connecting.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
using Elastic.Clients.Elasticsearch;
using Elastic.Transport;

var client = new ElasticsearchClient("<CLOUD_ID>", new ApiKey("<API_KEY>"));
```

