TITLE: Querying and Aggregating Project Data with Elasticsearch
DESCRIPTION: This Elasticsearch query retrieves project data, aggregates it by month, calculates commit counts, and applies bucket sorting. It uses a date histogram aggregation with a monthly interval and limits the results to the top 3 months by commit count.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch-net/blob/main/tests/Tests/_VerifySnapshots/BucketSortAggregationUsageTests.VerifyInitializerJson.verified.txt#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "aggregations": {
    "projects_started_per_month": {
      "aggregations": {
        "commits": {
          "sum": {
            "field": "numberOfCommits"
          }
        },
        "commits_bucket_sort": {
          "bucket_sort": {
            "from": 0,
