TITLE: KeyValuePair Collection Management
DESCRIPTION: Shows handling of ICollection<KeyValuePair<K, V>> types using fluent API patterns similar to dictionary operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch-net/blob/main/docs/release-notes/index.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
new PutMappingRequestDescriptor<Person>("index")
    .DynamicTemplates(new List<KeyValuePair<string, DynamicTemplate>>()) // Scalar.
    .DynamicTemplates(x => x                                             // Fluent: Nested.
        .Add("key", new DynamicTemplate())                               // Scalar: Key + Value.
        .Add("key", x => x.Mapping(new TextProperty()))                  // Fluent: Key + Value.
    )
    .AddDynamicTemplate("key", new DynamicTemplate())                    // Scalar: Key + Value.
    .AddDynamicTemplate("key", x => x.Runtime(x => x.Format("123")));
```

